description:
This is a 25 minute workout called '20 Minute Full Body Stretch | Deep Stretch for Total Body' from the channel Re:Align Pilates.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Get ready to feel SO GOOD after this deep full body stretch routine. ✨FREE 7-day trial to the Re:Align App: https://www.therealign.co/membership ✨ hundreds of exclusive workouts + nourishing recipes, sound healing meditations, and educational wellness workshops

Yoga Mat: https://amzn.to/3Sv1FxZ

Deanna Dorman is a celebrity Master Trainer, Fitness Nutrition Specialist, and Pilates instructor. Deanna has been featured in Shape, Self, Women's Health, Buzzfeed, and a number of other print and online publications as a leading fitness expert and healthy recipe developer. She is the creator and founder of The Re:Align Collective - an on-demand video app that delivers new workouts every week!
